## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="20a7f-132">此属性是以 y 轴比例的百分比进行度量。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="20a7f-132">This property is measured as a percentage of the Y-axis scale.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="20a7f-133">默认情况下，其值设置为 25。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="20a7f-133">By default, its value is set to 25.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="20a7f-134">这意味着，将使用刻度分隔线折叠数据点序列中具有至少 25%的比例的差异。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="20a7f-134">This means that data points in a series that have a difference of at least 25% of the scale will be collapsed with a scale break.</span></span>  
  
   
  
